category: X11
requires: libfreetype6 libgcc1 libGL1 libGLU1 libstdc++6
external-source: ftgl
sdesc: "OpenGL font rendering library (runtime)"
ldesc: "FTGL is a C/C++ library to enable developers to use arbitrary 
fonts in their OpenGL applications. FTGL uses the Freetype font library 
to open and decode the fonts. It then takes that output and stores it in 
a format most efficient for OpenGL rendering."
